Author: aceshighsays
Text: Yup! I have 4 days to lose 7 pounds. When I see my aunt on thanksgiving she will say something about my weight gain. She always does. I've never liked her bc she has no boundaries. I have 4 days to think of my response to her.

Author: ImNotaTreeImaShrub
Text: I relate so hard. I got down from 200lbs to 150lbs and fuck I've been stalled there for ages. Going back and forth between 155 and 145. I get down to 145 and then binge my way back up. I feel like I've lost my drive. I wanted to be 120lbs by now.   We can do this!
